    • createDefaultService

      public static SafariDriverService createDefaultService()
      Configures and returns a new SafariDriverService using the default configuration. In this configuration, the service will use the SafariDriver executable identified by the DriverFinder.getDriverPath() (DriverService, Capabilities)}. Each service created by this method will be configured to use a free port on the current system.
      Returns:
      A new SafariDriverService using the default configuration.
